Build a small library that can be used by different applications, that provides:

   Constants / Macros:
      CINIT_HALT
      CINIT_REBOOT
      CINIT_POWEROFF

      CINIT_SVC_NORMAL
      CINIT_SVC_NEEDS
      CINIT_SVC_ONLY
      CINIT_SVC_WANTS

   Functions:
      void cinit_halt(int how);
      int cinit_svc_start(char *svc, int how);
